{"tid":466827,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[心痛] 恒指已逐漸成為內地經濟的指標","createTime":"2017-11-13T02:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T10:05:11.000Z","uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"928b1156f74f68f619a06698cb4f02d399411338","tid":466827,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"隨著國泰航空遭剔出，恒指與本地經濟的關聯將進一步降低。在50隻藍籌之中，只餘少數地產股、銀行股以及公用股是以香港為業務基地，恒指已逐漸成為內地經濟的指標。國泰被換出，亦反映外資企業在恒指的比重下降，現時恒指只剩下滙豐控股（005）、金沙中國（1928）以及國泰母公司太古A（019）具歐美資金背景。<br />\n<br />\n睇見都心傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8947ec64f764e9c70627fae8b7d5dddebdd81d","tid":466827,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"一早紅到無人有啦"},{"pid":"2c666426b77e91ca7ca4b9bdd7b8381f6ea41588","tid":466827,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"都仲有長和既"},{"pid":"359c42052fd7055ff1098a011b3d74de9f64fa79","tid":466827,"uid":92064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"要騰訊carry你班垃圾,知唔知醜<br />\n走哂佢就岩"},{"pid":"d897686b4b1ff45825e99c291fab4f175f7b84ce","tid":466827,"uid":61222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"國泰佔恆指0.1%，有幾大影響力呀"},{"pid":"1071dc1ec70f7a86defaeb658510eb45afd64ecf","tid":466827,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都仲有長和既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日長和 明日太古"},{"pid":"0dcf2020cb3f4e529f515b46ee9bcde1554a7ec6","tid":466827,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}